#: core/templates/core/about.html:14
msgid ""
"En <strong>UNLABELED</strong>, creemos que la prenda debe hablar por sí "
"misma. Vivimos en la intersección del arte, la música alternativa y la "
"libertad absoluta."
msgstr ""
"At <strong>UNLABELED</strong>, we believe the garment should speak for "
"itself. We live at the intersection of art, alternative music, and "
"absolute freedom."

#: core/templates/core/about.html:19
msgid ""
"\"La identidad no se define por una marca, sino por la calidad de lo que "
"eliges vestir.\""
msgstr ""
"\"Identity is not defined by a brand, but by the quality of what you "
"choose to wear.\""

#: core/templates/core/about.html:23
msgid ""
"Nuestras colecciones son curadas detalladamente para ofrecer piezas "
"atemporales, sin logos visibles, enfocándonos únicamente en la manufactura y "
"los materiales premium."
msgstr ""
"Our collections are carefully curated to offer timeless pieces, with "
"no visible logos, focusing solely on manufacturing and premium materials."

